text: Lays Fernanda Oliveira de Freitas (born 13 October 1995) is a Brazilian volleyball player. She played at the 2016 Women's U22 South American Volleyball Championship, 2016 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U23 World Championship. == References == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian volleyball players
